I hope this helps, but if you have any questions or need any help activating your account, please don’t hesitate to get in touch.<br/><br/>

Finally, <b>if you are no longer interested</b> in being a Dementia Friends Champion, please send me an email and I will take you off our records.<br/><br/>

Best wishes,<br/>
